Author: TrashcanDarling
Text: Freaking out about going home for Christmas since I don't want people to see that I've lost weight.. especially my mom, she'll flip. Also I'm so stuck in my current eating habits that I have no fucking idea how to handle all the food that will be available at all times. I worry I'll go on a two week b/p rollercoaster.   I love the holidays but fuck me does having an ED complicate things.. a *lot*.
